snippet: PGA Tour Commissioner Tim Finchem said two British newspaper reports of a bid to take over the European Tour were inaccurate.
abstract: PGA Tour Commissioner Tim Finchem disputes two British newspaper reports of a bid by the PGA Tour to take over the European Tour, calling them inaccurate.
lead_paragraph: PGA Tour Commissioner Tim Finchem said two British newspaper reports of a bid to take over the European Tour were inaccurate.

headline.main: PGA Disputes Reports of European Acquisition
